data.description: Wow, what an absolute gem of a property! Welcome to country living! Beautifully maintained, charming painted brick home on almost 2 acres of land. Back half of property is fully privacy fenced in. 3BDR 3BA, w/ possibility for 2 additional bedrooms, living areas or flex spaces. One finished area off kitchen w/ a mini split & area that could be used as a closet or even an office. Basement has large unfinished portion great for storage and also a finished portion w/ one bedroom and second area that could be a bedroom, office, playroom or flex space. The possibilities are endless! This property also has an amazing 28'x40' wired shop that has a lean to on both sides that are the whole length of the shop, great for storing lawnmowers, yard equipment etc. NO HOA!! New roof 2 yrs ago, new HVAC 2 yrs ago, shop has new roof 3 yrs ago. Septic tank recently pumped. Convenient location approx. 5 miles to I85, restaurants & shopping. 3rd bedroom in basement has no emergency egress.
